name: MEOWICA BASEBALL TEE
description:
Meowica 'Domesticated and Fluffy' Cattery is printed on American Apparel 3/4 length raglan (baseball) tee. This fun parody design is based on the style of artwork used by the best Bay Area Thrash band Metallica, originally created by mighty Pushead. Print is washed-out for that retro 80/90s look.

Strictly limited to 30 shirts.

Finished with a "t" back print, and Tidy Shirts hem tag.

The t-shirts are a fitted size, and if like me you are not at the peak of your physical prowess, go for a size higher than normal.

Shipped worldwide via 'Signed For 1st Class' post. No returns due to limited stock, so please pick your size correctly.

name: CHRISTMAS CARDS
description:
Give your loved ones an original and beautifully crafted card for Christmas this year. Does you granny really need a burning church, or living dead Santa gift? hell yeah she does! 

Set of 5 alternative Christmas cards with 'Merry Christmas' printed inside. Individually wrapped in cellophane packet with ribbed, brown envelope.

Satan loves you.

name: ATTACK ATTACK! PRINT
description:
A2 (420x594mm) Digital Print, strictly limited to 50. From the Merch n' Destroy exhibition by t-shirt designer Sean Tidy. Signed by the artist.

All proceeds from the sale of this print will be donated to homeless charity Shelter From The Storm.

Prints will be posted after 14th November. All prints sent via 'Signed For 1st Class' in a cardboard tube. Worldwide delivery can take up to 3 weeks. Please be patient.
